  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269860</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_070_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>王としての責任を
果たせなかった非力さの罪を
あがなうため……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>As a King, he had no power to accomplish
what his people needed...So with that guilt
in his heart, he tried to make up for it...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269860</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_070_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だから、ダオスは
魔王と呼ばれても、
故郷のために戦った？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is that why he took on the role
of a Demon Lord? To make it
up to his people?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269992</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_070_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だから、犠牲をたくさん出してでも
『大いなる実り』を
故郷に持ち帰ろうとしたんだね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So to that end, he decided no matter the
number of victims, he needed to bring back
the Mana Seed to his home world.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270108</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_070_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そして、また同じ罪を
繰り返すかもしれない
オレらを消そうとした</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So that's what he meant by saying we could
repeat that same sin. After all, he was faced
with a similar situation once again.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270172</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_070_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ダオス……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Dhaos...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270340</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_070_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どうすんだ、&lt;Rody&gt;。
こっから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Rody&gt;, it's only a little further.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270640</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_070_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>もちろん、会いに行くよ、
ダオスに</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah, let's go meet with Dhaos...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270640</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_070_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>止めなきゃ、あの人を……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I need to put him to rest...</EnglishText>
      <Notes>TL check</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270640</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_070_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>もうこれ以上、
苦しまないでいいって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Or else he'll be suffering here forever...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270640</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_070_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ちゃんと
言ってあげなきゃ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I need to talk to him...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>3</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270640</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_070_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それに、双子ちゃんたちも
聞きたいことあるんでしょ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Besides, you twins have a lot
to hear from him too, right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>4</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270780</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_070_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>行こう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Let's go.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
